eval\npython3 rag/index/query_rag.py \"bilingual clinicians\" -k 5 --source website\n\n# Docs-only retrieval\npython3 rag/index/query_rag.py \"cross-platform content strategy\" -k 5 --source docs\n```\n\n## Current schema\nEach chunk includes:\n- `id`\n- `path`\n- `source_type` (`website` or `docs`)\n- `chunk_index`\n- `text`\n\n## Notes\n- This is a **working RAG v1** using lexical ranking (BM25), not embedding vectors yet.\n- It is deterministic and auditable, good for immediate production drafting.\n- Next upgrade path: add embedding vectors + hybrid retrieval (BM25 + vector rerank).\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/rag/RAG_OPERATOR_GUIDE.md\",\"content\":\"# Nava RAG Operator Guide (v1)\\n\\n## What exists now\\n- Unified chunk corpus: `rag/index/chunks.jsonl`\\n- Retrieval index (BM25 lexical): `rag/index/bm25_index.json`\\n- Build scripts:\\n  - `rag/index/build_chunks.py`\\n  - `rag/index/build_bm25.py`\\n- Query script:\\n  - `rag/index/query_rag.py`\\n\\n## Rebuild pipeline\\n```bash\\npython3 rag/index/build_chunks.py\\npython3 rag/index/build_bm25.py\\n```\\n\\n## Query examples\\n```bash\\n# Combined retrieval (website + docs)\\npython3 rag/index/query_rag.py \\\"healthcare staffing trust deficits\\\" -k 5\\n\\n# Website-only retrieval\\npython3 rag/index/query_rag.py \\\"bilingual clinicians\\\" -k 5 --source website\\n\\n# Docs-only retrieval\\npython3 rag/index/query_rag.py \\\"cross-platform content strategy\\\" -k 5 --source docs\\n```\\n\\n## Current schema\\nEach chunk includes:\\n- `id`\\n- `path`\\n- `source_type` (`website` or `docs`)\\n- `chunk_index`\\n- `text`\\n\\n## Notes\\n- This is a **working RAG v1** using lexical ranking (BM25), not embedding vectors yet.\\n- It is deterministic and auditable, good for immediate production drafting.\\n- Next upgrade path: add embedding vectors + hybrid retrieval (BM25 + vector rerank).\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-