 semantics.\n","new_string":"## Vector backend behavior\n- Preferred backend: `fastembed` (ONNX transformer; installed in `rag/.venv`).\n- Secondary backend: `ollama_embed` (`nomic-embed-text`) if local Ollama embedding endpoint is responsive.\n- Fallback backend: `fallback_hash_embedding` (stdlib-only signed hash vectors + char n-grams).\n- Why fallback exists: keeps retrieval operational in dependency-constrained environments.\n- Constraint: fallback is weaker than transformer embeddings on deep paraphrase semantics.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"rag/RAG_OPERATOR_GUIDE.md\",\"old_string\":\"## Vector backend behavior\\n- Preferred backend: `sentence-transformers` (if installed at build time).\\n- Fallback backend (implemented): `fallback_hash_embedding` using stdlib-only signed hash vectors + char n-grams.\\n- Why fallback exists: keeps retrieval operational in dependency-constrained environments.\\n- Constraint: fallback is weaker than transformer embeddings on deep paraphrase semantics.\\n\",\"new_string\":\"## Vector backend behavior\\n- Preferred backend: `fastembed` (ONNX transformer; installed in `rag/.venv`).\\n- Secondary backend: `ollama_embed` (`nomic-embed-text`) if local Ollama embedding endpoint is responsive.\\n- Fallback backend: `fallback_hash_embedding` (stdlib-only signed hash vectors + char n-grams).\\n- Why fallback exists: keeps retrieval operational in dependency-constrained environments.\\n- Constraint: fallback is weaker than transformer embeddings on deep paraphrase semantics.\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":71405,"output":241,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73182,"cost":{"input":0.12495875,"output":0.003374,"cacheRead":0.0002688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.12860155}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773767386477}}
